OL,3,CMonaco 'parcel bomb' explosion injures
OL,4,CUkrainian tycoon and family
OL,6,FLocal authorities said the attacker,
OL,7,Fwho had dumped a backpack full of
OL,8,Fbolts and pellets, fled to France.
OL,10,FMonaco's Prince Albert II called it an
OL,11,F"odious and heinous crime" and said
OL,12,Fall the country's state services were
OL,13,Fmobilised to ensure security.
