OL,3,CMonaco 'parcel bomb' explosion injures
OL,4,CUkrainian tycoon and family
OL,6,FThe attack on Monday night stunned the
OL,7,Felite principality on the
OL,8,FMediterranean Coast.
OL,10,FMinister of State Christophe Mirmand
OL,11,Ftold reporters the motive is under
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,F"This is the first time in history, to
OL,15,Fmy knowledge, that such an act has
OL,16,Ftaken place in the principality," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@aO]
