OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782836318
OL,3,CMonaco 'parcel bomb' explosion injures
OL,4,CUkrainian tycoon and family
OL,6,FThe explosion occurred around 9pm
OL,7,Flocal time at the entrance of a
OL,8,Fresidence near the French border,
OL,9,Finjuring two adults and a child who
OL,10,Fwere taken to hospitals in Nice, he
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FLe Figaro said CCTV shows a man
OL,14,Fdropping a backpack in the lobby of
OL,15,Fthe building shortly before the blast.
OL,17,FThe suspect is thought to have crossed
OL,18,Fthe border into France on foot, and
OL,19,Fwas identified via video surveillance
OL,20,Fin Monaco and the neighbouring French
OL,21,Ftown of Beausoleil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
