PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782836318
OL,3,CMonaco 'parcel bomb' explosion injures
OL,4,CUkrainian tycoon and family
OL,6,FA French national police official said
OL,7,Fofficers are searching for the suspect
OL,8,Fand supporting the investigation, but
OL,9,Fwould not elaborate.
OL,11,FFrench broadcaster BFM and Ukrainian
OL,12,Fnews site Ukrainska Pravda identified
OL,13,Fone of the injured as construction
OL,14,Ftycoon Yermolaiev.
OL,16,FIt was reported Yermolaiev had been
OL,17,Ftargeted by Ukrainian sanctions in
OL,18,F2023 for ties to Russia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
